    • readResults

      public static Vals readResults(String mdId, String period, String type, int start, int len)
      Returns normalized results of a directory.

      If results can not be read, returns 'r.date = ""' and 'r.Vals = []'

      Parameters:
      mdId - Model identifier.
      period - One of 'Cts.Periods'.
      type - One of 'cts.Types'.
      start - Index of the first date to return values.
      len - Number of dates to return values. NOTE: It can be returned less values if there is some error.
      Returns:
      Ditto.

    • rankValue

      public static Opt<Ival> rankValue(String mdId, String period, String type, int idate, String stats)
      Returns best value for global ranking.

      When 'stats=="deviation"' 'r.ix == 0', because r.val is an average.

      If the function fails, returns 'Opt.none()'.

      Parameters:
      mdId - Model identifier.
      period - Period index (one of 'Cts.Periods').
      type - Value types index (one of 'cts.Types').
      idate - date index (first is 0).
      stats - One of Cts.stats.
      Returns:
      Ditto.
